full_desc: If Q1e. MOCADIGI (attention - digits), Q1f. MOCALETT (attention - letter a), Q1g. MOCASER7 (attention - serial 7s), Q1h. MOCAREPE (language - repetition), Q1i MOCAFLUE (language - fluency), Q1j. MOCAABST (abstraction), Q1k. MOCARECN (delayed recall - no cue), Q1n. MOCAORDT (orientation - date), Q1o. MOCAORMO (orientation - month), Q1p. MOCAORYR (orientation - year), Q1q. MOCAORDY (orientation - day), Q1r. MOCAORPL (orientation - place), or Q1s. MOCAORCT (orientation - day) are between 95 and 98 then Q1d. MOCBTOTS (total raw score) must be 88
test_logic: MOCADIGI=95,96,97,98 or MOCALETT=95,96,97,98 or MOCASER7=95,96,97,98 or MOCAREPE=95,96,97,98 or MOCAFLUE=95,96,97,98 or MOCAABST=95,96,97,98 or MOCARECN=95,96,97,98 or MOCAORDT=95,96,97,98 or MOCAORMO=95,96,97,98 or MOCAORYR=95,96,97,98 or MOCAORDY=95,96,97,98 or MOCAORPL=95,96,97,98 or MOCAORCT=95,96,97,98 and MOCBTOTS not equal 88
comp_vars: MOCBTOTS, MOCADIGI, MOCALETT, MOCASER7, MOCAREPE, MOCAFLUE, MOCAABST, MOCARECN, MOCAORDT, MOCAORMO, MOCAORYR, MOCAORDY, MOCAORPL, MOCAORCT
